  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A tense situation at Fort railway station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the people who were inconvenienced by the cancellation of many trains since the morning of today (01) due to lack of fuel, are behaving restlessly at the Colombo Fort railway station.",
        "People who had booked seats earlier and boarded the train were severely inconvenienced and a large number of people are now staying at the Fort Railway Station.",
        "Due to this situation, station masters of Colombo Fort railway station resigned.",
        "The Fort Railway Station officials were severely inconvenienced as none of the Railway Department executives reported to the Colombo Fort Railway Station to control the unrest.",
        "The Railway Department, which serves as the main link in public transport, did not provide fuel to railway employees when they refueled due to non-designation of essential services, railway employees said."
      ],
